#<AdxTL>@(#)0.0.0.0 $Revision$
# Superviseur
# Gestion du masque NCSH1 

$_AFF
If GIMPORT
 Gosub AFF From GSAISIE
Else
 If GMESSAGE <>""
  Gosub ERR From GSAISIE
 Else
  Raz GERR , GZNUM
 Endif
Endif
Return

$ON_ZCHGMANUSR
Onevent BEFORE_AREA Gosub AV_ZCHGMANUSR From W2NCSH1
Return

$AV_ZCHGMANUSR
Call LECTEXTRA(zc,"AUTILIS","INTUSR",num$([M]CHGMANUSR(indice)),"") From ATEXTRA
Gosub _AFF
Return

$CHG_STY
Return


